%% Diagram: Cascading failure from a deep liveness probe
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant DB as Slow Dependency (DB)
    participant Pod as Service Pod
    participant Kube as kubelet (livenessProbe)
    participant LB as Load Balancer

    Note over DB,Pod: Database slows under load
    Kube->>Pod: GET /healthz (deep check)
    Pod->>DB: SELECT 1
    DB--xPod: timeout
    Pod-->>Kube: 503 / no response
    Kube->>Pod: SIGKILL + restart

    Note over Pod,LB: Capacity drops by 1 replica
    LB->>Pod: redirect requests to surviving pods
    Pod->>DB: more queries per pod
    DB--xPod: queries get slower

    Note over Kube: Repeats across replicas
    loop For each replica
        Kube->>Pod: GET /healthz
        Pod--xKube: timeout
        Kube->>Pod: restart
    end

    Note over DB,LB: Outage: every replica restarting on a sick dependency
